{"id": "art-1537", "label": "Art. 1537", "title": "Art. 1537", "slug": "art-1537", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_881074414\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2109\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_881074414\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 153<sup>7</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_58435067\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2108\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_58435067\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)În cazul <span class=SpellE>vacan&#355;ei</span> unui\npost de membru în consiliul de supraveghere, consiliul poate proceda la numirea\nunui membru provizoriu, pân&#259; la întrunirea adun&#259;rii generale.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1531793982\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2107\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1531793982\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Dac&#259; <span class=SpellE>vacan&#355;a</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>men&#355;ionat&#259;</span> la alin. (1) determin&#259;\nsc&#259;derea num&#259;rului membrilor consiliului de supraveghere sub minimul\nlegal, directoratul trebuie s&#259; convoace f&#259;r&#259; întârziere adunarea\ngeneral&#259; pentru completarea locurilor vacante.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2047638783\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2106\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2047638783\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)În cazul în care directoratul nu <span class=SpellE>î&#351;i</span>\n<span class=SpellE>îndepline&#351;te</span> <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;ia</span>\nde a convoca adunarea general&#259; în conformitate cu alin. (2), orice parte\ninteresat&#259; se poate adresa <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;ei</span> pentru\na desemna persoana îns&#259;rcinat&#259; cu convocarea adun&#259;rii generale\nordinare a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>, care s&#259; fac&#259;\nnumirile necesare.</span></p>"}